{"id": "ChIJdfiEi8m4woAR82sc6js_AXs", "rating": 4.4, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_EXPENSIVE", "userRatingCount": 468, "displayName": {"text": "Kali Steak", "languageCode": "en"}, "editorialSummary": {"text": "Minimalist & chic space for seasonal & contemporary California cuisine, plus eclectic wines.", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJdfiEi8m4woAR82sc6js_AXs/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tsc05IQmhjSEp0Y2xWaVlYWjNOMmM0WDNsRVpGRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "We loved this restaurant when visiting LA. Definitely recommend the park house rolls, and the steak was cooked perfectly. The staff was very kind and attentive. We loved the chocolate dessert. Everything we had from the mocktails to the dessert was top notch. Definitely recommend visiting if you’re in the area!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "We loved this restaurant when visiting LA. Definitely recommend the park house rolls, and the steak was cooked perfectly. The staff was very kind and attentive. We loved the chocolate dessert. Everything we had from the mocktails to the dessert was top notch. Definitely recommend visiting if you’re in the area!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Kaitlyn Copeland", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103195546667517893450/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXAg4vepliyQaC7S7ab_NfC3g7EKntlRSGS8L_-EMMvqzQJhEk-=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-06T23:15:59.810438636Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tsc05IQmhjSEp0Y2xWaVlYWjNOMmM0WDNsRVpGRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tsc05IQmhjSEp0Y2xWaVlYWjNOMmM0WDNsRVpGRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2b8c98b84f875:0x7b013f3bea1c6bf3"}, {"name": "places/ChIJdfiEi8m4woAR82sc6js_AXs/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pJdFpVMWpNM1JSWTAxelEyOVZXR05pWkVkcGJuYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "This place was super good. The service was amazing and the food was great. Our server Amanda was a great help. And the Original Kali Meringue Gelato was one of the best desserts I have ever had. I highly recommend that one. Our server said that was the item that won them the Michelin star.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "This place was super good. The service was amazing and the food was great. Our server Amanda was a great help. And the Original Kali Meringue Gelato was one of the best desserts I have ever had. I highly recommend that one. Our server said that was the item that won them the Michelin star.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Zach Carlson", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111169911234487557234/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ5-28wysEIVEZhWD8krKxHz-UlEdVmO7e0ZMrL7Ortm9JZeA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-31T02:22:59.346783266Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pJdFpVMWpNM1JSWTAxelEyOVZXR05pWkVkcGJuYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pJdFpVMWpNM1JSWTAxelEyOVZXR05pWkVkcGJuYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2b8c98b84f875:0x7b013f3bea1c6bf3"}, {"name": "places/ChIJdfiEi8m4woAR82sc6js_AXs/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pKZmNrWmZOazVtT1hkaVdqVkJXRjlwYURWTGFsRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 2, "text": {"text": "It’s a steakhouse, but the quality of the steak and the cooking were not up to standard. Even though we ordered the steak medium, it was cooked closer to medium-well. When we pointed this out to the supervisor, he refused to acknowledge the issue. We were left feeling quite helpless—being told it could be remade, but we didn’t want to waste more time waiting again. At checkout, there was also no acknowledgment or gesture from the restaurant; however, as we were very hungry and had already finished the meal, we felt it was awkward to raise the issue again.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "It’s a steakhouse, but the quality of the steak and the cooking were not up to standard. Even though we ordered the steak medium, it was cooked closer to medium-well. When we pointed this out to the supervisor, he refused to acknowledge the issue. We were left feeling quite helpless—being told it could be remade, but we didn’t want to waste more time waiting again. At checkout, there was also no acknowledgment or gesture from the restaurant; however, as we were very hungry and had already finished the meal, we felt it was awkward to raise the issue again.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "xinyi chen", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114130529665342410302/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKkM_qtmE15xBzrkzpC2iPUYrWAn6Hlf4UfjCNcMXtKGtb6tw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-18T20:12:37.304341210Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pKZmNrWmZOazVtT1hkaVdqVkJXRjlwYURWTGFsRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pKZmNrWmZOazVtT1hkaVdqVkJXRjlwYURWTGFsRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2b8c98b84f875:0x7b013f3bea1c6bf3"}, {"name": "places/ChIJdfiEi8m4woAR82sc6js_AXs/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tweVVtaHNkVWt6U1VVeWRXTmlabEl4TWtWb1JYYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "6 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Loved the food. I had the mushroom risotto. I highly recommend it!\nThe atmosphere was a bit darker than I'd like, but then I saw Kumail Nanjiani with his wife Emily Gordon casually dining and thought, \"How awesome it this?!!? So, perfect. Only in LA!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Loved the food. I had the mushroom risotto. I highly recommend it!\nThe atmosphere was a bit darker than I'd like, but then I saw Kumail Nanjiani with his wife Emily Gordon casually dining and thought, \"How awesome it this?!!? So, perfect. Only in LA!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Natalia Ventura", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102587848762372476826/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUJRgUWzZ-8EozRuaPO5FsG06He2NF3_DwEICyilBge23Zq76xqYQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2025-12-24T15:37:35.703968986Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tweVVtaHNkVWt6U1VVeWRXTmlabEl4TWtWb1JYYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tweVVtaHNkVWt6U1VVeWRXTmlabEl4TWtWb1JYYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2b8c98b84f875:0x7b013f3bea1c6bf3"}, {"name": "places/ChIJdfiEi8m4woAR82sc6js_AXs/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21oNVYwZzVXRTl0ZUhkUlltNXNhWHAyY0U5S1JsRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Classic style steakhouse, with great service, excellent selection of awesome steaks, and great cocktails. If you don't want to drop a mint on dinner, the bar bites menu is pretty reasonable with some interesting and delicious options. Highly recommend for a nice dinner", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Classic style steakhouse, with great service, excellent selection of awesome steaks, and great cocktails. If you don't want to drop a mint on dinner, the bar bites menu is pretty reasonable with some interesting and delicious options. Highly recommend for a nice dinner", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Scott Patton", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/113336303656731543267/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ-1R-hf